{
  "thought": "先搜索 GitHub 仓库来测试 search_repositories 工具，搜索一个热门项目如 'react'，观察返回结果。",
  "action": "tool_call",
  "tool_name": "github__search_repositories",
  "tool_args": {
    "query": "react",
    "perPage": 3
  }
}

{
  "thought": "搜索成功！看到了 react 官方仓库、TypeScript 速查表等。接下来测试 get_file_contents，读取 react 仓库的 README.md。",
  "action": "tool_call",
  "tool_name": "github__get_file_contents",
  "tool_args": {
    "owner": "react",
    "repo": "react",
    "path": "README.md"
  }
}

{
  "thought": "成功读取了 React 仓库的 README.md。接下来测试 search_code，搜索 GitHub 上使用 'useState' 的代码片段。",
  "action": "tool_call",
  "tool_name": "github__search_code",
  "tool_args": {
    "q": "useState language:typescript",
    "per_page": 3
  }
}

